            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">This equates to 2% potato matter and 98% water as expected. Therefore, we need to<strong> dehydrate the potatoes by 50 pounds</strong> in order to obtain 98 percent water!</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
