            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">And that’s why it’s called a <em>paradox</em>. It seems like in order to reduce the weight by 1 percent we wouldn’t have to dehydrate them much at all. But in fact we have to <strong>reduce the weight by half of the original!</strong></p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
